org.pathvisio.core.data

Class XrefWithSymbol

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pathvisio.core.data.XrefWithSymbol
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<XrefWithSymbol>

    public final class XrefWithSymbol
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<XrefWithSymbol>
    Stores a combination of DataSource, id and symbol. See also Xref, which only stores DataSource and id. A symbol is a name or biological shorthand that is not guaranteed to be unique or unambiguous

    Immutable class, thread-safe
